    "title": "Opinion Announcement - June 19, 1997",
    "transcript": {
        "title": null,
        "duration": 179.406,
        "sections": [
            {
                "start": 0,
                "stop": 179.406,
                "byte_start": 28672,
                "byte_stop": 746203,
                "turns": [
                    {
                        "start": 0,
                        "stop": 8.132,
                        "byte_start": 28672,
                        "byte_stop": 61273,
                        "speaker": null,
                        "text_blocks": [
                            {
                                "start": 0,
                                "stop": 8.132,
                                "byte_start": 28672,
                                "byte_stop": 61273,
                                "text": "A new record Number 96-663, Klehr versus A.O. Smith Corporation would be announced by Justice Breyer."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 8.132,
                        "stop": 179.406,
                        "byte_start": 61273,
                        "byte_stop": 746203,
                        "speaker": null,
                        "text_blocks": [
                            {
                                "start": 8.132,
                                "stop": 20.642,
                                "byte_start": 61273,
                                "byte_stop": 111323,
                                "text": "This case involves a suit under civil RICO, a -- a statute that provides treble damages and attorneys fees for those injured by a \u201cpattern of racketeering activity.\u201d"
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 20.642,
                                "stop": 25.407,
                                "byte_start": 111323,
                                "byte_stop": 130341,
                                "text": "The words \u201cpattern of racketeering activity\u201d are terms of art."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 25.407,
                                "stop": 32.338,
                                "byte_start": 130341,
                                "byte_stop": 158030,
                                "text": "Racketeering activity, it means this commission of certain defined predicate acts."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 32.338,
                                "stop": 40.598,
                                "byte_start": 158030,
                                "byte_stop": 191154,
                                "text": "Each act is a violation of some other statute like the statute that forbids murder or fraud or robbery et cetera."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 40.598,
                                "stop": 50.502,
                                "byte_start": 191154,
                                "byte_stop": 230755,
                                "text": "And a pattern means among other things the commission of at least two predicate acts separated in time one from the other by no more than ten years."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 50.502,
                                "stop": 60.273,
                                "byte_start": 230755,
                                "byte_stop": 269834,
                                "text": "So if you had two acts of fraud separated in time by a few months or even a few years, they could count possibly as a RICO violation."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 60.273,
                                "stop": 66.529,
                                "byte_start": 269834,
                                "byte_stop": 294808,
                                "text": "Now, the plaintiffs in this case were dairy farmers who bought a silo for storing feed for their cows."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 66.529,
                                "stop": 81.785,
                                "byte_start": 294808,
                                "byte_stop": 355830,
                                "text": "They say that the seller of the silo told them falsely and fraudulently that the silo meant healthier cows because it would prevent oxygen from getting to the feed and preventing and -- which might cause mold or fermentation and all that they said was false."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 81.785,
                                "stop": 83.538,
                                "byte_start": 355830,
                                "byte_stop": 362830,
                                "text": "That isn\u0027t what happened at all."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 83.538,
                                "stop": 96.993,
                                "byte_start": 362830,
                                "byte_stop": 416747,
                                "text": "Now, their problem is that they have a serious statute of limitations problem because they bought the silo 19 years before they brought suit and the statute of limitations is supposed to be four years under the Clayton Act."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 96.993,
                                "stop": 101.217,
                                "byte_start": 416747,
                                "byte_stop": 433570,
                                "text": "But the plaintiffs has pointed out it all depends on when that four-year period starts running."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 101.217,
                                "stop": 103.4,
                                "byte_start": 433570,
                                "byte_stop": 442347,
                                "text": "That\u0027s called the Accrual Date."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 103.4,
                                "stop": 126.574,
                                "byte_start": 442347,
                                "byte_stop": 535030,
                                "text": "And one of these Circuits have said that the action doesn\u0027t -- it doesn\u0027t start to run until the last predicate act and that really is the issue we primarily face and we said, \u201cWell, we don\u0027t agree with that Circuit\u0027s rule because the statute then might run sometimes forever for a very long time anyway and it\u0027s not consistent with Clayton Act authority.\u201d"
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 126.574,
                                "stop": 135.403,
                                "byte_start": 535030,
                                "byte_stop": 570347,
                                "text": "Now, there are other differences in other Circuit rules but we haven\u0027t reached those because none of them would affect the plaintiffs before."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 135.403,
                                "stop": 137.691,
                                "byte_start": 570347,
                                "byte_stop": 579438,
                                "text": "The plaintiffs raised one additional matter."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 137.691,
                                "stop": 143.138,
                                "byte_start": 579438,
                                "byte_stop": 601276,
                                "text": "They said that the seller fraudulently concealed the fraud."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 143.138,
                                "stop": 151.937,
                                "byte_start": 601276,
                                "byte_stop": 636489,
                                "text": "Use for example a device that shoot up the feed just when it came out of the silo so you wouldn\u0027t notice the mold and various other things."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 151.937,
                                "stop": 172.735,
                                "byte_start": 636489,
                                "byte_stop": 719663,
                                "text": "They said this fraudulent concealment should stole -- toll the statute of limitations; it should stop the clock; but the lower court found that they weren\u0027t reasonably diligent in looking out for the fraud and the issue before us really was whether reasonable diligence is a requirement in order to get the tolling and we hold that it is."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 172.735,
                                "stop": 174.787,
                                "byte_start": 719663,
                                "byte_stop": 727918,
                                "text": "So we affirm the lower court judgment."
                            },
                            {
                                "start": 174.787,
                                "stop": 179.406,
                                "byte_start": 727918,
                                "byte_stop": 746203,
                                "text": "Justice Scalia filed a concurring opinion in which Justice Thomas concurs."
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        ]
    },
